    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一套令人上头的多巴胺循环玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >钓到鱼，只是开始。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抛下鱼线，寻找那条最完美的猎物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为鱼刮鳞，但要小心别刮坏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卖掉猎物，把收益投入升级。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断下潜，捕捉更大、更怪异的鱼类。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次升级，都会把你推向更深的海域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/2fd23d9ea2280d3a66fa167f115deba0.poster.avif?t=1771857548\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/2fd23d9ea2280d3a66fa167f115deba0.webm?t=1771857548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/2fd23d9ea2280d3a66fa167f115deba0.mp4?t=1771857548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>四大世界，惊喜不断</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索四个风格迥异的世界，每个都源自真实地点，并拥有独特的：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >环境与氛围</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鱼类生态</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏秘密</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一张地图都暗藏惊喜，从隐秘地点到解谜机关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/19011883d29f0c274c1bfa5d7f3278b0.poster.avif?t=1771857548\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/19011883d29f0c274c1bfa5d7f3278b0.webm?t=1771857548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/19011883d29f0c274c1bfa5d7f3278b0.mp4?t=1771857548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>口味各异、性格鲜明的“非人类”顾客</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的顾客并非人类，而是来自神话与传说的生物，比如尼斯湖水怪、凯尔派，以及更多意想不到的访客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摸清他们的喜好，把对的鱼卖给对的客人，才能赚得更多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/924de179c8ddaf854c3036ff4477cfa9.poster.avif?t=1771857548\" width=1170 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/924de179c8ddaf854c3036ff4477cfa9.webm?t=1771857548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/924de179c8ddaf854c3036ff4477cfa9.mp4?t=1771857548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>秘密与宝藏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深海中不只有鱼，探索欲会得到回报。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏的宝藏与可收集的遗物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >漂流瓶里的信息</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >环境谜题与机关装置</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果某样东西看起来不对劲，那它多半真的不对劲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/ccfdca8437a07aa3327dbd5ad780bc23.poster.avif?t=1771857548\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/ccfdca8437a07aa3327dbd5ad780bc23.webm?t=1771857548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/ccfdca8437a07aa3327dbd5ad780bc23.mp4?t=1771857548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打造你的船只，用风格征服深海</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成长不只是数值提升。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级你的钓鱼装备：更长的鱼线、更好的鱼饵、更深的潜行能力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义你的船只外观</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁角色外观装饰</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为探索深海、喂养古老生物，也应该<i>足够有型</i>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/f96b940e1eb7137691b748479db43159.poster.avif?t=1771857548\" width=1170 height=660 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/f96b940e1eb7137691b748479db43159.webm?t=1771857548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3198890/extras/f96b940e1eb7137691b748479db43159.mp4?t=1771857548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
